  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A comparison between local and intraperitoneal analgetics to placebo, during laparoscopy,
      regarding post operative pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      4 randomly assigned groups. Grop 1 will get sub cutaneous and intraperitoneal marcain. Grop 2
      will get sub cutaneous marcaine and intraperitoneal saline. Grop 3 will get sub cutaneus
      saline and intraperitoneal marcaine. Grop 4 will get ub cutaneous and intraperitoneal saline
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
